I feel like this season has been an uphill battle because none of my race outcomes matched the expectations I had. I’ve been struggling a lot with the mental aspect that comes with this sport and I’m working on that. I’m still growing and learning as I go. I know what I’m capable of and I will get there at the right time. 

Rejoice in hope, be patient in tribulation, be constant in prayer - Romans 12:12

Also, I’m forever grateful for my support systems and everyone who has been following my journey. You all mean the world to me.🫶🏼
